These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, soy-milk
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, white, brown
1. the person who likes white is the person drinking lemonade##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is between the person who likes brown and the person drinking lemonade##2
3. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who likes blood-red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Beverage      | lemonade | soy-milk | juice |
| Color   | white     | blood-red    | brown   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
House: cape-cod, art-deco, ranch-style
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the cape-cod house is on the left of the ranch-style house##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the cape-cod house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| House   | cape-cod    | ranch-style        | art-deco |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: iris, zinnia, bellflower
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the person who growsiris is between the owner of the ferret and the person who growsbellflower##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Flower   | zinnia | iris     | bellflower |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
There are 3 different nationalities: egyptian, indian, nigerian
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the egyptian is the owner of the bird##1
2. the nigerian is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Nationality   | indian  | nigerian     | egyptian |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: fantasy, thriller, superhero
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | superhero     | fantasy |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, jet-ski, skateboard
1. the person driving the roller is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Transport         | jet-ski | roller | skateboard |

