The people have 3 different jobs:  engineer, architect, security-guard
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the engineer is between the person eating pineapple and the architect##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
