.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: ice-hockey, swimming, weightlifting
There are 3 different favourite beverages: cola, water, mirinda
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person drinking water##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | swimming  |
| Beverage   | mirinda    | cola        | water |

