1. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Sport         | golf | rowing | surfing |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | car    | motorbike |

