.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: orange, lilac, emerald
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person who likes lilac and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person who likes emerald is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Color   | lilac | orange      | emerald      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

