.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
House: gothic-revival, victorian, farmhouse
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, gospel, punk
1. the gothic-revival house is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the victorian house is between the farmhouse house and the fan of gospel##2
3. the fan of disco is on the right of the farmhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| House      | farmhouse | victorian   | gothic-revival |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | disco | gospel   |

 